  "title": "10 Footer Lorry Driver | Choa Chu Kang / Tengah Office",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><em><strong>Class 3 Small Truck Driver [ Lorry Driver ] - Manual</strong></em></p></li><li><p><strong>Landscaping & Plantation Company</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>5.5 Days, 8am-5pm (Mon to Fri) | 8am to 12pm (Sat)</strong></p></li><li><p><em><strong>Basic Salary: $2,300 - $2,500</strong></em><strong> + Bonus</strong></p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Office at Tengah Area [ Choa Chu Kang ], Singapore</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Entitled to Medical Benefits & Bonus</strong></p></li></ul><p><br /><u><em><strong>Remarks: Drive 10 Footer Lorry, Class 3, Manual Type</strong></em></u></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li><p><strong>Class 3 driving license, driving small truck or lorry</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Min 2 years of driving experience is required for this role</strong></p></li></ol><p><strong>Job Scopes:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Adhere to assigned schedule and ensure work tasks are completed on time.</p></li><li><p>Transporting workers and goods to sites.</p></li><li><p>Collecting and disposing of rubbish from work sites.</p></li><li><p>Safely securing heavy loads and large goods for transport.</p></li><li><p>Organizing the most efficient route from pickup point to drop off point.</p></li><li><p>Organizing multiple drop-offs and deliveries in each working day.</p></li><li><p>Support landscape and hydroculture maintenance work.</p></li><li><p>Upkeep assigned company vehicle: routine checking of engine; & general cleanliness.</p></li><li><p>Ensuring vehicles are mechanically sound and legally roadworthy.</p></li><li><p>Immediately complete and submit accident reports (e.g., injuries) to your manager.</p></li><li><p>Supervising and assisting with the loading and unloading of deliveries into the lorry.</p></li><li><p>Complying with all LTA and in-house regulations and rule.</p></li><li><p>Other duties and responsibilities as assigned.<br /></p></li></ul><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p><p><br />\n\n</p>",
